							<img src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Screen-Shot-2021-02-09-at-10.43.33-AM-100x100.png" width="96" height="96" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2021/02/Screen-Shot-2021-02-09-at-10.43.33-AM-300x300.png 2x" alt="Rebecca Morgan Frank" class="avatar avatar-96 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-96 alignnone photo" />						</div>
